            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="45138647">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在公共秩序中按国家利益的标准（不管多么不精确）来限制良心自由，是一种来自共同利益即平等的公民代表的利益原则的限制。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-22 15:16</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote>在公共秩序中按国家利益的标准（不管多么不精确）来限制良心自由，是一种来自共同利益即平等的公民代表的利益原则的限制。</blockquote><p></p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/45138647/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2017-06-22 15:16
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>
